<HEADLINE>
<P>
BORDER DITCH CONTROVERSY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Only time will tell whether the controversial border ditch will really reduce 
drug and illegal alien traffic from Mexico. But, the arrogance and hypocrisy of 
the Mexican government in opposing the project is outrageous. 
</P>
<P>
The ditch will be entirely on U.S. land. It will have absolutely no effect on 
aliens who are in the U.S. legally, or on any legitimate commerce between the 
two countries. But, it will hurt the drug lords and the coyotes who deal in 
human misery. 
</P>
<P>
Let's dig the ditch! It's worth a try! 
</P>
<P>
BILL ROSENTHAL 
</P>
<P>
Huntington Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
