<TEXT>
<P>
I am shocked and amazed at the senselessness and duplicity of Mike Downey's 
"Having a Field Day" column. It had absolutely nothing to do with the world of 
sports; and was a self-serving and misguided attempt at satire, fueled in large 
part by the womanizing of two politicians and a preacher. 
</P>
<P>
