<HEADLINE>
<P>
LAZERS PLAY DALLAS TODAY AT FORUM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Lazers, losers of two straight, will play host to the Dallas Sidekicks 
today at 1:30 at the Forum. 
</P>
<P>
It has been nearly a week since the Lazers (16-17) last played a Major Indoor 
Soccer League game, losing to the San Diego Sockers, 8-1, in falling six games 
behind the first-place Baltimore Blast. 
</P>
<P>
The Lazers haven't fared too well against Dallas, either. The Sidekicks 
(16-16), a half-game ahead of the Lazers, have won four of five meetings this 
season. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030489-0083 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 26292 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 4, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
